    ],
    "text": "Special Operation Targeting Unroadworthy Vehicles \u2013 Nuwara Eliya Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      154.69,
      544.34,
      195.57
    ],
    "text": "On 25.02.2026, officers from the Nuwara Eliya Police Station, together with officials of the Department of Motor Traffic, conducted a special vehicle inspection operation within the Nuwara Eliya Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      210.01,
      535.12,
      237.09
    ],
    "text": "The operation was carried out in the Haggala area along the Nuwara Eliya\u2013Badulla Road and in the Boralanda area on the Nuwara Eliiya\u2013Udupussellawa Road.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      251.68,
      543.26,
      292.56
    ],
    "text": "During the inspection, prohibition notices were issued to 49 vehicles found to be unfit for road use due to poor maintenance and unsatisfactory condition. These included 18 passenger buses, 21 lorries, 8 motorcycles, and 2 three-wheelers.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
